PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant (a) an EASEMENT (ES-800) to the REGIONAL MUNICIPALITY OF OTTAWA-CARLETON, for a term of ninety-nine (99) years, and (b) the two temporary LICENCES OF OCCUPATION it requires for the installation of sewer works under those N.C.C. properties situated along its 7.5 kilometre path from a point at Walkley Road, Ottawa, north to a point at the Queensway in Gloucester (SOUTH OTTAWA COLLECTOR).
